A4.text: Located in the Alaska Range in the interior of the U.S. state of Alaska, Denali is the centerpiece of Denali National Park and Preserve.

A5.text: The Koyukon people who inhabit the area around the mountain have referred to the peak as 'Denali' for centuries.
